        "image": "file:///Users/kiki/Desktop/ki%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92/exam/listening/immediate-response/n1/assets/images/2013.7-1.png",
        "dialogueHtml": "<span class=\"speaker-text\">ねえ、<ruby>会計課<rt>かいけいか</rt></ruby>の<ruby>山田<rt>やまだ</rt></ruby><ruby>君<rt>くん</rt></ruby>、いつも<span class=\"keyword\" onclick=\"showTooltip(event, 'ぼそぼそ：\\n拟声拟态词。形容说话声音很小、低声嘟囔、自言自语的样子。通常给人一种听不清、没精神的负面印象。')\">ぼそぼそ</span><ruby>話<rt>はな</rt></ruby>すよね。</span>",
